		"txt":"[{\"instruction\":\"For the initial scenario of such applications, a lightweight deployment solution is often adopted, and a configuration with small-sized and low-bandwidth servers can meet the business demands, enabling the operation of such services as applications and databases. As the websites/application access increase and the services become more diversified, the cloud server instance types and scale can be adjusted rapidly to elastically adjust the resource allocation based on the service cycle, thus elastically improving the computing capability with low costs.\",\"name\":\"Enterprise Website/Web Application/Mobile APP\",\"picUrl\":\"//img1.jcloudcs.com/cms/30a00344-9b7e-49aa-8597-3d24dff542c620170421160301.jpg\",\"selectedProduct\":[],\"buttons\":{\"name\":\"\",\"link\":\"\",\"classTag\":\"\"},\"showShade\":false},{\"instruction\":\"In the practical massive picture/video applications (such as large e-commerce website), the Virtual Machines, in combination with Load Balancer, Object Storage Service cloud storage and CDN, can substantially shorten the access waiting time while saving costs for the users.\",\"name\":\"Mass picture/video and other applications\",\"picUrl\":\"//img1.jcloudcs.com/cms/d7ff1070-2106-469c-8f21-acce80be143620171205150124.jpg\",\"selectedProduct\":[],\"buttons\":{\"name\":\"\",\"link\":\"\",\"classTag\":\"\"},\"showShade\":false}]",
